description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Best Exercise For Pregnant Women | 30-Minute Pregnancy Exercises For Easy Delivery' from the channel Pregnancy and Postpartum TV.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: I get asked all the time for a the best exercise for pregnant women.  "You have so many videos...Is there just one that I can do daily?" Today's video is a routine with a little of everything to keep you and your baby healthy and prepare for an easy delivery! We will warm up, get the heart pumping with cardio, do some hip openers, asymmetrical poses, pelvic floor and core work and get baby is an optimal fetal position.  I hope you feel great after these pregnancy exercises! Safe for first trimester, second trimester and third trimester!
